          "type": "thinking",
          "thinking": "Now I understand the policy framework:\n\n1. **Split reimbursement rule (第十一条)**: \n   - Cannot split the same or similar items into multiple reimbursements to avoid approval limits.\n   - Same employee, same expense type, within 7 days, 2+ reimbursements whose total amount reaches the \"较高审批线\" (higher approval tier).\n   - The approval tiers per the authorization management attachment:\n     - AR-01: 0-2999 - department manager\n     - AR-02: 3000-9999 - department manager + financial review\n     - AR-03: 10000-49999 - department general manager\n     - AR-04: 50000-199999 - deputy general manager (分管副总)\n     - AR-05: >=200000 - general manager office meeting\n\n2. The \"较高审批线\" - I interpret this as a significant approval threshold. Looking at the tiers, I'd say AR-03 (10000元) or higher is a \"较高审批线\" since it requires department general manager approval. But let me think more carefully...\n\n   Actually, the policy says \"合计金额达到《授权管理办法》附件二较高审批线的\". A \"较高审批线\" would be a line that requires higher-level approval. Looking at AR-03 (10000元, department general manager), AR-04 (50000元, deputy general manager), AR-05 (200000元, general manager office meeting) - these are progressively higher.\n\n   Let me check the policy excerpt more carefully:\n   \"同一员工、同一费用类型在7天内出现2笔及以上报销,且合计金额达到《授权管理办法》附件二较高审批线的,应重点核查拆分规避审批。\"\n\n   So within 7 days, same employee, same expense type, 2+ reimbursements with combined amount reaching one of the higher approval tiers in the authorization management attachment.\n\nI think the \"较高审批线\" would mean at least AR-03 (10000元, requires department general manager) or higher. Let me now look at the expense data.\n\nThe task says \"全年数据做拆分报销专项扫描\" - full year scan for split reimbursement. So I need to check all expense records for the full year (2025 or relevant year).\n\nLet me start by listing all employees and expenses.",
          "signature": ""
        },
