          "type": "thinking",
          "thinking": "With 4240 records, I need a more efficient approach. Let me think about what the policy says:\n\n第十一条: 同一员工、同一费用类型在7天内出现2笔及以上报销,且合计金额达到较高审批线的,应重点核查拆分规避审批。\n\nFor \"较高审批线\", looking at the authorization table:\n- AR-03: >=10000 and <50000 (部门总经理)\n- AR-04: >=50000 and <200000 (分管副总)\n- AR-05: >=200000 (总经理办公会)\n\nI think AR-03 (10000元) is a \"较高审批线\" since it requires department general manager approval. So if a same employee has 2+ reimbursements of the same type within 7 days, and the total amount >= 10000, that's a potential split.\n\nLet me also check the business entertainment policy:",
